¡In memory of Jim and Bet Harris, who spent many happy hours here
Jim Harris 2.2.1910-15.3.2004
Bet Harris 24.3.1911-1.6.2008

(Pat-Maureen and Joe-Graham and Pauline-John, husband of Linda)"Œ
ÀGeorge 'Uncle Boy' Clasper
01.07.1927-09.01.2009
Much loved brother and uncle who loved to walk his dogs in this park
The years in our eye we can wipe away
But the pain in our hearts will always stay"ÿ
’WALTER LEARY
17th Feb.1920 - 23rd Dec.1994
COUNCILLOR ST.KATHERINE'S WARD 1964-1985
Kingdoms may come, Kingdoms may go
Whatever the end may be
But Old Father Thames keeps rolling along
Down to the mighty sea"€
